{"tid":1323794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：鄭若驊訪京四日　將晤司法部、外交部","createTime":"2019-07-16T11:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T11:33:04.000Z","uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d776dc42575c579fbea283cc34df41b46c97cc2b","tid":1323794,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"政府公布，負責逃犯條例修訂的律政司司長鄭若驊，明日下午（周三）前赴北京，本月 20 日（周六）返港，在北京期間，鄭若驊將與司法部、外交部、最高人民法院代表會面，以及參觀北京互聯網法院。她亦會出席第二次「一帶一路」聯席會議。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊與保安局長李家超負責的逃犯條例修訂，引起巨大爭議，雖然特首林鄭月娥指修例「壽終正寢」，但連場衝突、遊行等仍未平息。<br />\n<br />\n脫離港大民意研究計劃獨立運作的香港民意研究所，公布首次民意調查結果，其中律政司司長鄭若驊的評分再跌至 21.6分，是歷來最低評分官員。前公務員事務局局長王永平表示，保安局長李家超和律政司長鄭若驊二人應該顧全大局，考慮辭職。"},{"pid":"f16dd00eae70c8e439e52d0f311cfd672fbf1121","tid":1323794,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"Source：<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E8%A8%AA%E4%BA%AC%E5%9B%9B%E6%97%A5-%E5%B0%87%E6%99%A4%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeWaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=bf59d58c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%2599%25A4%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%2F&h=75db20b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E8%A8%AA%E4%BA%AC%E5%9B%9B%E6%97%A5-%E5%B0%87%E6%99%A4%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8/</a>"},{"pid":"32d0bbbbfc07b1a2ab62e946519d172c2b229d33",